                        <div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;margin-left: 1em;">(30) $136,000 to the Vida Mobile Clinic, for the Vida Mobile Clinic Outreach &amp; Medical Supplies.</div>
                        <div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;margin-left: 1em;">(31) $1,250,000 to Bridge to Home Santa Clarita Valley, for the Bridge to Home Family Housing Units &amp; Client Service Center.</div>
                        <div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;margin-left: 1em;">(32) $1,000,000 to the City of Orange, for the City of Orange: Homeless Resource Center.</div>
