                        <div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;margin-left: 1em;">(43) $2,000,000 for the County of Fresno for design and construction costs of improvements in the communities of Cantua Creek and
                           El Porvenir.
                        </div>
                        <div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;margin-left: 1em;">(44) $240,000 for Habitat for Humanity Greater Fresno Area for program support.</div>
                        <div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;margin-left: 1em;">(45) $150,000 for the City of Reedley for improvements to transitional housing facility.</div>
