                           of the Ghostship Warehouse fire.
                        </div>
                        <div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;margin-left: 1em;">(61) $2,000,000 for St. Mary’s Center for property acquisition, maintenance, and operations for transitional housing for formerly
                           homeless seniors.
                        </div>
                        <div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;margin-left: 1em;">(62) $2,500,000 for the Los Angeles Black Worker Center for the establishment of
